<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id90b8b927-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s6434"><num value="6434">§ 6434.</num><heading> Applicability of other laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Chapter 10 of title 5 shall not apply to the Commission.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id90b8b928-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/105/292/tII/s206">Pub. L. 105–292, title II, § 206</ref>, formerly § 204, <date date="1998-10-27">Oct. 27, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2799">112 Stat. 2799</ref>; renumbered § 206, <ref href="/us/pl/106/55/s1/b/2">Pub. L. 106–55, § 1(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="1999-08-17">Aug. 17, 1999</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/113/401">113 Stat. 401</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/286/s4/a/172">Pub. L. 117–286, § 4(a)(172)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-27">Dec. 27, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/4324">136 Stat. 4324</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id90b8b929-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id90b8b92a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id90b8b92b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/105/292/s206">section 206 of Pub. L. 105–292</ref> was renumbered section 209 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s6436">section 6436 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id90b8b92c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2022—<ref href="/us/pl/117/286">Pub. L. 117–286</ref> substituted “Chapter 10 of title 5” for “The Federal Advisory Committee Act (5 U.S.C. App.)”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
